:0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T11:15:18.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"5277f2fc9eee631db6923bf40ee78926626ec650","tid":504700,"uid":88374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T11:25:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>人眼睇日出日落都咁靚，睇空氣折射日光都咁靚<br />\n<br />\n如果人眼可以睇埋d紫外線，甚至伽瑪射線，星塵既光，超新星爆炸發出既電磁波，<br />\n<br />\n呢個宇宙一定好精彩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人眼只係睇緊光譜既咁少百分比，真係可惜</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果可以睇到微觀世界的東西，微細昆蟲、細菌、細胞、病毒、基因、有機分子、無機分子、原子、核子、電子、中子、質子、夸克、中微子，咁呢個宇宙都會相當精彩。<br />\n<br />\n如果你眼可以仔細望到每一顆行星、恒星、星系（如銀行系）。甚至可以睇到各行星的動態細節，睇到有沒有生命甚至微生命，呢個宇宙會相當相當精彩。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/21/192501_eff5cde7beaf921dd5c9367ab3770ec0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F21%2F192501_eff5cde7beaf921dd5c9367ab3770ec0.jpg&h=4d096d94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a998bc9ed049461a5822274cc183754a791577e3","tid":504700,"uid":3255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T11:32:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>wifi望到眼都花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n喂喂 你閂咗個wifi先啦 好燦眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2522710ce19811f85652aaf2e3b791df19c76a40","tid":504700,"uid":95452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T11:41:17.000Z","msg":"螳螂蝦咪睇到咁多隻色，咁人睇到多d色應該無咩問題"},{"pid":"84f612978cda43a1a4a49da06f7d496fdec46668","tid":504700,"uid":117679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T11:42:00.000Z","msg":"「光」嘅強度⋯唔係因為佢嘅頻率。唔係頻率越高就越光⋯<br />\n<br />\n所以唔會因爲你見到所有「光」嘅頻譜而覺得燦眼⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n同埋我地見到唔同顏色，係由於可見光光譜入面某啲頻率被物件吸收。所以我地只係見到餘下反射入去我地眼嘅頻譜，所混合而成嘅顏色。唔係因為我地直接望到啲光。可見光加埋係透明。係望唔到。<br />\n<br />\n呢啲係中學教㗎咋⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31de6b8f6ab8d521076d86d750de289113fe47a9","tid":504700,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T11:43:11.000Z","msg":"個個都話d wifi會好燦眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我講緊望上夜空會好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d40dbb65afdfb4d9fd91694c5747cc89abd9b290","tid":504700,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T11:44:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>「光」嘅強度⋯唔係因為佢嘅頻率。唔係頻率越高就越光⋯<br />\n<br />\n所以唔會因爲你見到所有「光」嘅頻譜而覺得燦眼⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n同埋我地見到唔同顏色，係由於可見光光譜入面某啲頻率被物件吸收。所以我地只係見到餘下反射入去我地眼嘅頻譜，所混合而成嘅顏色。唔係因為我地直接望到啲光。<span style=\"color: red;\">可見光加埋係透明。係望唔到。</span><br />\n<br />\n呢啲係中學教㗎咋⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nis it real<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0431dda8195767031cb2477ffd3f8acd08fcb380","tid":504700,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T11:44:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個個都話d wifi會好燦眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我講緊望上夜空會好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n凡事有得必有失"},{"pid":"7eedc041bb5e8951c4b996511e334bc1fddd27c3","tid":504700,"uid":81354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T11:46:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個個都話d wifi會好燦眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我講緊望上夜空會好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n宇宙幅射多到你唔會想睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ac8f8a605252f60675bc797aaa8545522a077e0","tid":504700,"uid":103983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T11:53:08.000Z","msg":"假設望住一個發熱物體<br />\n你同時見到infrared red,visible light<br />\n咁你隻眼係見到邊一種<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /